A thug has been found guilty of breaking the jaw of a student during the riots.

Beau Isagba, who also has convictions for carrying a blade and cannabis possession, wept as he heard he faced a long prison sentence.

The 17-year-old can now be named after the judge took the unusual step of lifting reporting restrictions due to the public interest in the case after the student’s ordeal was seen by millions of people on YouTube.

